David Tutera se vrača s še več nevestami, ki obupno potrebujejo pomoč pri poročnem dnevu. Nekatere neveste želijo obleko iz risank, okrasje v slogu merlota, polne mize kristalov in srednjeveško zabavo. David ima ogromno dela, ko spreminja katastrofalne zamisli v prekrasne poroke.

David Tutera is back, with more brides in desperate need of a wedding day do over. There are brides who want Little Bo Peep dresses, décor based on merlot wine, tables dripping with crystals, or medieval-themed parties. David’s got his work cut out transforming these calamitous celebrations into wonderful weddings.

V seriji Polnočna pojedina vam bo italijanski oddelek za hrano v New Yorku predstavil epski polnočni kulinarični obračun med nekaterimi najboljšimi vrhunskimi kuharji v državi. V vsaki edinstveni epizodi se bodo štirje kuharji pomerili v treh krogih z izločanjem, v katerih bodo morali pripraviti predjed, glavno jed in sladico. V vsakem krogu bodo kuharji imeli na voljo katerekoli sestavine, ki jih bodo našli na oddelku s hrano in zelo malo časa za načrtovanje in pripravo jedi. Po vsakem krogu bodo sodniki ocenili jedi glede na predstavitev, okus in ustvarjalnost ter izločili enega kuharja iz tekmovanja. Na koncu bo zmagovalec dobil denarno nagrado, ki predstavlja dvojno vrednost njegovega računa, poraženec pa bo moral plačati svoj račun. Ker imajo dostop do najboljših sestavin na svetu, mora vsak kuhar premisliti, ali je vredno tvegati in pripravljati jedi s temi dragimi in eksotičnimi sestavinami, saj ga sotekmovalec lahko porazi. Samo najbolj drzni in ustvarjalni kuharji bodo lahko premagali tri nasprotnike v treh krogih in si zaslužili slavo in denarno nagrado. Spremljali boste najbolj zahtevno bitko bistrih umov, ustvarjalnosti in veščin, ki jo je kulinarični svet kadarkoli videl.

In MIDNIGHT FEAST, a NYC food-hall (think Eataly) sets the stage for an epic late-night culinary showdown between some of the hottest professional chefs in the country. In each stand-alone episode, 4 chefs go head to head in 3 rounds of elimination: "munchies", "main", and "sweets." In each round, the chefs are given free rein to use any ingredient found in the food hall but have minimal time to plan and execute each dish. After each round, the judges critique the dishes based on presentation, taste, and creativity and cut one chef from the competition. By the end of the night, the winner walks away with a cash prize (twice the cost of their grocery bill!) while the losers walk away paying their own tabs. With access to the finest ingredients in the world, each chef must weigh their desire to use the most expensive and exotic ingredients against the risk of picking up an outlandish bill. Only the most daring and creative chefs will be able to beat three rivals over three courses to win glory and a cash prize. It's the most grueling battle of wits, creativity and skill the food world has ever seen.

V tej resničnostni oddaji spremljamo življenje in posle Katrine Campins, nekdanje zvezde oddaje "Apprentice" in vrhunske nepremičninske agentke iz Miamija. Campinsova skrbi za več kot 350 znanih osebnosti, za športnike in bogate zvezdnike kot so Russell Brand, Katy Perry in Justin Timberlake. Posle vodi z očarljivim bivšim možem, nadzorovalno kubansko mamo in s svojo mlajšo sestro. Gledalci dobijo vpogled v dramo, ki se odvija med delom, ko pomaga strankam kupiti in prodati luksuzne nepremičnine v vročem Miamiju. Od plaže do sejne sobe, serija sledi Katrini in njeni ekipi nepremičninskih agentov med raziskovanjem najbolj luksuznih nepremičnin v Miamiju.

This reality series features the life and business of Katrina Campins, former "Apprentice" star and successful high-end Miami real estate agent. Campins caters to over 350 A-list celebrities, athletes and wealthy professionals, including Russell Brand, Katy Perry and Justin Timberlake. She runs her business with her charming ex-husband, her controlling Cuban mother and her younger sister. Viewers get an inside look at the drama behind helping high-end clients buy and sell luxury real estate in sultry Miami. From the beach to the boardroom, the series will follow Katrina and her team of realtors as they explore Miami's most luxurious properties.

Da bi naredili prvi korak v svet nepremičnin, prvotne kupce ponavadi zanimajo soseske, ki so izgubile svoj ugled. Njihova ustvarjalnost vodi v obnovo krajevnih sosesk, jih iz pozabljenih spremeni v izjemne in jim tako povrne ponos ter njihovo vrednost v skupnosti, ki jih obdaja. V seriji bomo spremljali štiri nadarjene pare, ki bodo tekmovali med seboj v modernih prenovah domov. Poiskali bomo mesto ali kraj, od Buffala do Baltimora, ki je na samem robu uspeha. Vsak par bo dobil v prenovo vrstno hišo. V tem času bo živel v zapuščenem domu in dobil omejena sredstva, da bo lahko preuredil prostore. Končni cilj je povečati vrednost doma, kolikor je to le mogoče. Na koncu pa bodo pari pokazali svoje delo sosedom, ki so ves čas vohunili in ugotavljali, kateri par se je odrezal najbolje.

To take that first critical step onto the property ladder, first-time homebuyers often explore neighborhoods that have lost their luster. Their creativity leads the renovation of local neighborhoods, taking them from forgotten, to fabulous, and restoring the pride and property value of the community surrounding them. "Renovation Row" is a format that pits four talented renovation couples against each other in an on-trend transformation showdown. We will cast a town or city - from Buffalo to Baltimore - that is on the verge of becoming "the next big thing." Each couple will be given one rowhouse to renovate over the course of our series. While living inside these dilapidated homes our couple will use a designated budget to re-do key rooms and spaces in each self-contained episode. The final goal is to increase the overall value of the home by as much as they can. In the finale, the couples will stage an open house for their homes, and our neighborhood families - who have been spying on these newcomers and sharing their opinions with them all along - will have a chance to see the new homes on their street and witness which couple has increased the value to the max.

Pridružite se čudovitim južnjaškim nevestam, ki iščejo svojo popolno poročno obleko. V največjem poročnem salonu v Ameriki, Stardust Celebrations, si ogledamo trud teksaških nevest, ki zapravijo na tisoče dolarjev, in osebje, ki se trudi uresničiti njihove sanje o poročni obleki.

Join some extraordinary Southern Brides on their amazing quest for the perfect wedding dress. At the largest bridal salon in America – Stardust Celebrations – we follow the lengths to which Texas Brides will go, the thousands of dollars they will pay and the staff who’ll stop at nothing make their wedding gown dreams come true!

Spoznajte Kenyatto Jones, oblikovalko in direktorico znamke Bella René. Svojo znamko bi rada spremenila v modno ikono, a se zdi, da se ne zna ogniti drami doma in v službi. Njena mama ima mnenje o vsem, fant ne počne nič, zaposleni pa ne znajo biti tiho, zato ima Kanyatta veliko dela.

Meet Kenyatta Jones, designer and CEO of Bella René clothing. While she’s hustling to turn Bella René into a fashion powerhouse, she can’t seem to find a way to get around the drama at work and home. With her opinionated mom, deadbeat boyfriend, and staff members who can’t seem to keep their thoughts to themselves, Kenyatta has her hands full.

V novi seriji FYI-ja spremljamo glamurozni najboljši prijateljici Emily Dees Boulden in Nicole Noles na avanturi po Ameriki, kako postavljata trende na svojem vročem fenomenu na štirih kolesih – na modnem poltovornjaku. V vsaki epizodi poskrbita za stilsko preobrazbo modno neosveščenih prebivalcev. Najprej pa se odpravita v trgovino modnih specialistov, da napolnita tovornjak s trendovskimi oblačili, in tako poučita gledalce o lokalnem stilu, kulturi in trendih.

In FYI's new series, GET SWANK'D, glam besties, Emily Dees Boulden and Nicole Noles, go on a trend-setting road trip adventure across America in the hottest phenomenon on wheels, a fashion truck. In each episode, Emily and Nicole will arrive at a location with a mission to perform makeovers on fashion-challenged locals. In order to stock their truck and give FYI viewers a crash course in local style, culture and trends, Emily and Nicole will take a shopping trip to a nearby store only known to fashion pros.

Join Beverly Hills, 90210's Shannen Doherty and fiancé photographer Kurt Iswarienko for a challenging, comical, and dramatic series about two people – with two different backgrounds – coming together. Their complicated, often hilarious, story is a picture of modern celebrity lifestyle, including wedding preparations, a house tragedy that threatens lawsuits, and the next chapter of the actress’ burgeoning career.

Pridružite se svetovno znanemu kuharskemu mojstru Marcu Thuetu ter njegovi ženi in poslovni partnerici Biani Zorich, ki zastavita svoj ugled za visokoleteči izziv, ki bo njiju in njune učence prignal do skrajnosti.

What do you get when you take one of the country’s top chefs, throw in 24 ex-cons with no culinary experience, and give them just three weeks to open a high-end restaurant from scratch? Join world-renowned executive chef Marc Thuet and his wife and business partner Biana Zorich as they put their reputations on the line with a high-stakes challenge that will push them—and their charges—to the limit.

Najbolj znana ženitna posrednica na svetu se je vrnila boljša kot kdajkoli prej! V tej sezoni Zmenkov milijonarjev Patti Stanger in njena ekipa ljubezenskih gurujev prevzame hotel Luxe in se loti najtežjih primerov ženitnega posredovanja. Vsak teden se bosta dve od najbolj zahtevnih strank prijavili v ekskluzivni Klub milijonarjev. Patti bo skupaj s svojima najboljšima posrednikoma Candace in Maxwellom vodila milijonarje skozi intenzivni petdnevni tečaj o težavah na zmenkih in pri iskanju prave ljubezni. Tretjo generacijo posrednikov čaka težko delo, saj jo stranke, vključno s seksi zvezdniki iz Real Housewives in The Bachelor, ne ubogajo. Bodo s pomočjo bolečih ampak iskrenih nasvetov milijonarji odšli iz hotela sami ali z novo ljubeznijo?

The world’s most renowned matchmaker is back and better than ever! On this season on Million Dollar Matchmaker, Patti Stanger and her team of love gurus take over the Luxe Hotel to take on the toughest cases in matchmaking history yet. Each week, two of the most challenging clients will check into the exclusive Millionaire’s Club. Patti, along with her top matchmakers Candace and Maxwell, will guide the millionaires through an intensive, five day, crash course to work through their dating issues and to find true love. The third generation matchmaker has her work cut out for her when clients including sexy singles from The Real Housewives and The Bachelor don’t abide by her rules! With tougher love and some much needed reality checks, will the millionaires check out alone or with a new found flame?

Smrti zvezdnikov so, podobno kot njihova življenja, lahko sporne, neverjetne in dramatične. Ko zvezdnik umre, vse, kar je dosegel v svojem življenju, ostane. Raziskali bomo smrti nekaterih zvezdnikov in kaj se je zgodilo z njihovim denarjem. Presenečenja nikoli niso daleč, kadar gre za zvezdnike. Celebrities’ deaths—much like their lives—can be controversial, fascinating and full of drama. When a celebrity dies, everything they’ve amassed during their lives—their fame, their accomplishments, and their possessions, stays behind. Celebrities Legacies explores what happens to these possessions. We explore the deaths of these celebrities and the big money involved in their passing. Surprises are always around the corner when stars are involved. This fascinating series details who tried to lay claim to the inheritance, who actually got it, what lavish-living celebrities really died penniless, and which celebrities are still making the highest-paid lists years after their deaths.

V seriji Polnočna pojedina vam bo italijanski oddelek za hrano v New Yorku predstavil epski polnočni kulinarični obračun med nekaterimi najboljšimi vrhunskimi kuharji v državi. V vsaki edinstveni epizodi se bodo štirje kuharji pomerili v treh krogih z izločanjem, v katerih bodo morali pripraviti predjed, glavno jed in sladico. V vsakem krogu bodo kuharji imeli na voljo katerekoli sestavine, ki jih bodo našli na oddelku s hrano in zelo malo časa za načrtovanje in pripravo jedi. Po vsakem krogu bodo sodniki ocenili jedi glede na predstavitev, okus in ustvarjalnost ter izločili enega kuharja iz tekmovanja. Na koncu bo zmagovalec dobil denarno nagrado, ki predstavlja dvojno vrednost njegovega računa, poraženec pa bo moral plačati svoj račun. Ker imajo dostop do najboljših sestavin na svetu, mora vsak kuhar premisliti, ali je vredno tvegati in pripravljati jedi s temi dragimi in eksotičnimi sestavinami, saj ga sotekmovalec lahko porazi. Samo najbolj drzni in ustvarjalni kuharji bodo lahko premagali tri nasprotnike v treh krogih in si zaslužili slavo in denarno nagrado. Spremljali boste najbolj zahtevno bitko bistrih umov, ustvarjalnosti in veščin, ki jo je kulinarični svet kadarkoli videl.

In MIDNIGHT FEAST, a NYC food-hall (think Eataly) sets the stage for an epic late-night culinary showdown between some of the hottest professional chefs in the country. In each stand-alone episode, 4 chefs go head to head in 3 rounds of elimination: "munchies", "main", and "sweets." In each round, the chefs are given free rein to use any ingredient found in the food hall but have minimal time to plan and execute each dish. After each round, the judges critique the dishes based on presentation, taste, and creativity and cut one chef from the competition. By the end of the night, the winner walks away with a cash prize (twice the cost of their grocery bill!) while the losers walk away paying their own tabs. With access to the finest ingredients in the world, each chef must weigh their desire to use the most expensive and exotic ingredients against the risk of picking up an outlandish bill. Only the most daring and creative chefs will be able to beat three rivals over three courses to win glory and a cash prize. It's the most grueling battle of wits, creativity and skill the food world has ever seen.

Meet Kenyatta Jones, designer and CEO of Bella René clothing. While she’s hustling to turn Bella René into a fashion powerhouse, she can’t seem to find a way to get around the drama at work and home. With her opinionated mom, deadbeat boyfriend, and staff members who can’t seem to keep their thoughts to themselves, Kenyatta has her hands full.

In this series David gets the shock of his life when Hollywood icon Tori Spelling asks to be his apprentice. Saturday nights in Las Vegas host one of the hottest, most competitive culinary battles in the country... Hidden from the public eye, until now! In this self-contained food competition format, two of Las Vegas's most elite, five-star chefs engage in a culinary game of epicurean proportions. Smrti zvezdnikov so, podobno kot njihova življenja, lahko sporne, neverjetne in dramatične. Ko zvezdnik umre, vse, kar je dosegel v svojem življenju, ostane. Raziskali bomo smrti nekaterih zvezdnikov in kaj se je zgodilo z njihovim denarjem. Presenečenja nikoli niso daleč, kadar gre za zvezdnike. Ta odlična serija predstavlja, kdo je hotel terjati dediščino, kdo jo je dejansko dobil, kateri zvezdniki, ki so živeli razkošna življenja, so umrli brez prebite pare in kateri zvezdniki se tudi leta po svoji smrti uvrščajo na sezname najbolje plačanih ljudi.

Celebrities’ deaths—much like their lives—can be controversial, fascinating and full of drama. When a celebrity dies, everything they’ve amassed during their lives—their fame, their accomplishments, and their possessions, stays behind. Celebrities Legacies explores what happens to these possessions. We explore the deaths of these celebrities and the big money involved in their passing. Surprises are always around the corner when stars are involved. This fascinating series details who tried to lay claim to the inheritance, who actually got it, what lavish-living celebrities really died penniless, and which celebrities are still making the highest-paid lists years after their deaths.

Najbolj znana ženitna posrednica na svetu se je vrnila boljša kot kdajkoli prej! V tej sezoni Zmenkov milijonarjev Patti Stanger in njena ekipa ljubezenskih gurujev prevzame hotel Luxe in se loti najtežjih primerov ženitnega posredovanja. Vsak teden se bosta dve od najbolj zahtevnih strank prijavili v ekskluzivni Klub milijonarjev. Patti bo skupaj s svojima najboljšima posrednikoma Candace in Maxwellom vodila milijonarje skozi intenzivni petdnevni tečaj o težavah na zmenkih in pri iskanju prave ljubezni. Tretjo generacijo posrednikov čaka težko delo, saj jo stranke, vključno s seksi zvezdniki iz Real Housewives in The Bachelor, ne ubogajo. Bodo s pomočjo bolečih ampak iskrenih nasvetov milijonarji odšli iz hotela sami ali z novo ljubeznijo?

The world’s most renowned matchmaker is back and better than ever! On this season on Million Dollar Matchmaker, Patti Stanger and her team of love gurus take over the Luxe Hotel to take on the toughest cases in matchmaking history yet. Each week, two of the most challenging clients will check into the exclusive Millionaire’s Club. Patti, along with her top matchmakers Candace and Maxwell, will guide the millionaires through an intensive, five day, crash course to work through their dating issues and to find true love. The third generation matchmaker has her work cut out for her when clients including sexy singles from The Real Housewives and The Bachelor don’t abide by her rules! With tougher love and some much needed reality checks, will the millionaires check out alone or with a new found flame?

Kaj se zgodi, ko vzamete enega najboljših kuharjev v državi in ga združite s 24 nekdanjimi zaporniki, brez kuharskih izkušenj ter jim daste tri tedne časa, da odprejo vrhunsko restavracijo? Pridružite se svetovno znanemu kuharskemu mojstru Marcu Thuetu ter njegovi ženi in poslovni partnerici Biani Zorich, ki zastavita svoj ugled za visokoleteči izziv, ki bo njiju in njune učence prignal do skrajnosti.

V seriji Polnočna pojedina vam bo italijanski oddelek za hrano v New Yorku predstavil epski polnočni kulinarični obračun med nekaterimi najboljšimi vrhunskimi kuharji v državi. V vsaki edinstveni epizodi se bodo štirje kuharji pomerili v treh krogih z izločanjem, v katerih bodo morali pripraviti predjed, glavno jed in sladico. V vsakem krogu bodo kuharji imeli na voljo katerekoli sestavine, ki jih bodo našli na oddelku s hrano in zelo malo časa za načrtovanje in pripravo jedi. Po vsakem krogu bodo sodniki ocenili jedi glede na predstavitev, okus in ustvarjalnost ter izločili enega kuharja iz tekmovanja. Na koncu bo zmagovalec dobil denarno nagrado, ki predstavlja dvojno vrednost njegovega računa, poraženec pa bo moral plačati svoj račun. Ker imajo dostop do najboljših sestavin na svetu, mora vsak kuhar premisliti, ali je vredno tvegati in pripravljati jedi s temi dragimi in eksotičnimi sestavinami, saj ga sotekmovalec lahko porazi. Samo najbolj drzni in ustvarjalni kuharji bodo lahko premagali tri nasprotnike v treh krogih in si zaslužili slavo in denarno nagrado. Spremljali boste najbolj zahtevno bitko bistrih umov, ustvarjalnosti in veščin, ki jo je kulinarični svet kadarkoli videl.

In MIDNIGHT FEAST, a NYC food-hall (think Eataly) sets the stage for an epic late-night culinary showdown between some of the hottest professional chefs in the country. In each stand-alone episode, 4 chefs go head to head in 3 rounds of elimination: "munchies", "main", and "sweets." In each round, the chefs are given free rein to use any ingredient found in the food hall but have minimal time to plan and execute each dish. After each round, the judges critique the dishes based on presentation, taste, and creativity and cut one chef from the competition. By the end of the night, the winner walks away with a cash prize (twice the cost of their grocery bill!) while the losers walk away paying their own tabs. With access to the finest ingredients in the world, each chef must weigh their desire to use the most expensive and exotic ingredients against the risk of picking up an outlandish bill. Only the most daring and creative chefs will be able to beat three rivals over three courses to win glory and a cash prize. It's the most grueling battle of wits, creativity and skill the food world has ever seen.

Celebrities’ deaths—much like their lives—can be controversial, fascinating and full of drama. When a celebrity dies, everything they’ve amassed during their lives—their fame, their accomplishments, and their possessions, stays behind. Celebrities Legacies explores what happens to these possessions. We explore the deaths of these celebrities and the big money involved in their passing. Surprises are always around the corner when stars are involved. This fascinating series details who tried to lay claim to the inheritance, who actually got it, what lavish-living celebrities really died penniless, and which celebrities are still making the highest-paid lists years after their deaths.

Lastnika podjetja Property Brothers, Drew in Jonathan Scott, uporabljata tako mišice kot možgane, da najdeta in obnovita neverjetne sanjske domove. Drew je postaven nepremičninski strokovnjak, ki išče skrite dragulje med hišami z neverjetnim potencialom, njegov brat dvojček Jonathan pa zna dolgočasno notranjost spretno spremeniti do nerazpoznavnosti. Skupaj sta brata zelo očarljiva in duhovita, ko pomagata družinam poiskati, ugodno kupiti in predelati hiše v izjemno prijetne sanjske domove.

Property Brothers Drew and Jonathan Scott combine brawn with brains in their quest to find and fix up incredible dream homes. Drew is the handsome real estate expert who tracks down hidden gems of houses that have untapped potential. His identical twin brother Jonathan is the handy contractor who overhauls their drab interiors with ambitious renovations. Together, the Property Brothers use plenty of charm and humor as they help families find, buy, and transform extreme fixer-uppers into the ultimate budget-friendly dream home.

Da bi naredili prvi korak v svet nepremičnin, prvotne kupce ponavadi zanimajo soseske, ki so izgubile svoj ugled. Njihova ustvarjalnost vodi v obnovo krajevnih sosesk, jih iz pozabljenih spremeni v izjemne in jim tako povrne ponos ter njihovo vrednost v skupnosti, ki jih obdaja. V seriji bomo spremljali štiri nadarjene pare, ki bodo tekmovali med seboj v modernih prenovah domov. Poiskali bomo mesto ali kraj, od Buffala do Baltimora, ki je na samem robu uspeha. Vsak par bo dobil v prenovo vrstno hišo. V tem času bo živel v zapuščenem domu in dobil omejena sredstva, da bo lahko preuredil prostore. Končni cilj je povečati vrednost doma, kolikor je to le mogoče. Na koncu pa bodo pari pokazali svoje delo sosedom, ki so ves čas vohunili in ugotavljali, kateri par se je odrezal najbolje.

To take that first critical step onto the property ladder, first-time homebuyers often explore neighborhoods that have lost their luster. Their creativity leads the renovation of local neighborhoods, taking them from forgotten, to fabulous, and restoring the pride and property value of the community surrounding them. "Renovation Row" is a format that pits four talented renovation couples against each other in an on-trend transformation showdown. We will cast a town or city - from Buffalo to Baltimore - that is on the verge of becoming "the next big thing." Each couple will be given one rowhouse to renovate over the course of our series. While living inside these dilapidated homes our couple will use a designated budget to re-do key rooms and spaces in each self-contained episode. The final goal is to increase the overall value of the home by as much as they can. In the finale, the couples will stage an open house for their homes, and our neighborhood families - who have been spying on these newcomers and sharing their opinions with them all along - will have a chance to see the new homes on their street and witness which couple has increased the value to the max.

Najbolj znana ženitna posrednica na svetu se je vrnila boljša kot kdajkoli prej! V tej sezoni Zmenkov milijonarjev Patti Stanger in njena ekipa ljubezenskih gurujev prevzame hotel Luxe in se loti najtežjih primerov ženitnega posredovanja. Vsak teden se bosta dve od najbolj zahtevnih strank prijavili v ekskluzivni Klub milijonarjev. Patti bo skupaj s svojima najboljšima posrednikoma Candace in Maxwellom vodila milijonarje skozi intenzivni petdnevni tečaj o težavah na zmenkih in pri iskanju prave ljubezni. Tretjo generacijo posrednikov čaka težko delo, saj jo stranke, vključno s seksi zvezdniki iz Real Housewives in The Bachelor, ne ubogajo. Bodo s pomočjo bolečih ampak iskrenih nasvetov milijonarji odšli iz hotela sami ali z novo ljubeznijo?

The world’s most renowned matchmaker is back and better than ever! On this season on Million Dollar Matchmaker, Patti Stanger and her team of love gurus take over the Luxe Hotel to take on the toughest cases in matchmaking history yet. Each week, two of the most challenging clients will check into the exclusive Millionaire’s Club. Patti, along with her top matchmakers Candace and Maxwell, will guide the millionaires through an intensive, five day, crash course to work through their dating issues and to find true love. The third generation matchmaker has her work cut out for her when clients including sexy singles from The Real Housewives and The Bachelor don’t abide by her rules! With tougher love and some much needed reality checks, will the millionaires check out alone or with a new found flame?

Sobotni večeri v Las Vegasu gostijo eno izmed najbolj vročih in tekmovalnih kulinaričnih bitk v državi, ki je bila skrita očem javnosti vse do zdaj! V tem edinstvenem tekmovanju se dva izmed najbolj priznanih šefov v Las Vegasu pomerita v kulinarični igri epikurejskih dimenzij. Uporabila bosta raznolike in eksotične sestavine, ki so jih pozabili krajevni ulični prodajalci hrane, prav tako bosta tovornjakom s hrano dovolila, da vstopijo v njuni odlično opremljeni in ogromni kuhinji, kjer bo vsak poskušal premagati svojega nasprotnika. Izjemne jedi bodo predstavljene dvema strokovnima sodnikoma, zmagovalec pa bo domov odnesel pravico do hvaljenja in čudovito trofejo!

Saturday nights in Las Vegas host one of the hottest, most competitive culinary battles in the country... Hidden from the public eye, until now! In this self-contained food competition format, two of Las Vegas's most elite, five-star chefs engage in a culinary game of epicurean proportions. Using a diverse and exotic range of ingredients left behind by local food truck vendors, these chefs leave their well-equipped, massive kitchens to enter never-before-seen food trucks where they will try to outwit, out-create and out-cook their rival. Extraordinary dishes are conceived and presented to two expert judges, with the winner taking home the ultimate Vegas foodie bragging rights and one fabulously large trophy!

Kaj se zgodi, ko vzamete enega najboljših kuharjev v državi in ga združite s 24 nekdanjimi zaporniki, brez kuharskih izkušenj ter jim daste tri tedne časa, da odprejo vrhunsko restavracijo? Pridružite se svetovno znanemu kuharskemu mojstru Marcu Thuetu ter njegovi ženi in poslovni partnerici Biani Zorich, ki zastavita svoj ugled za visokoleteči izziv, ki bo njiju in njune učence prignal do skrajnosti.

What do you get when you take one of the country’s top chefs, throw in 24 ex-cons with no culinary experience, and give them just three weeks to open a high-end restaurant from scratch? Join world-renowned executive chef Marc Thuet and his wife and business partner Biana Zorich as they put their reputations on the line with a high-stakes challenge that will push them—and their charges—to the limit.

Biti oče in partner v sveži zvezi, povrhu pa še načrtovati dogodke za petične zvezdnike je neizprosno, a Davidu Tuteri vseeno uspeva. Oborožen s svojim prepoznavnim stilom, hitro jezo in prebrisanostjo mora organizirati rodee za petdesetletnike, zabave za predstavitev spodnjega perila in družinska zbiranja sredstev. Vedno pa ga čaka težavna naloga, saj mora spremeniti divje zahteve strank v epske zabave.

With 50th birthday rodeos, spectacular lingerie launches and family fundraisers to organise, and armed only with his trademark style, wit and short fuse, David’s got a real job on his hands turning wild demands into epic celebrations.

Pridružite se Shannen Doherty iz serije Beverly Hills 90210 in fotografu Kurtu Iswarienku ter si oglejte duhovito in dramatično serijo, polno izzivov, v kateri boste spoznali dva človeka z dvema različnima ozadjema, ki stopita na skupno pot. Their complicated, often hilarious, story is a picture of modern celebrity lifestyle, including wedding preparations, a house tragedy that threatens lawsuits, and the next chapter of the actress’ burgeoning career.

Campinsova skrbi za več kot 350 znanih osebnosti, za športnike in bogate zvezdnike kot so Russell Brand, Katy Perry in Justin Timberlake. Gledalci dobijo vpogled v dramo, ki se odvija med delom, ko pomaga strankam kupiti in prodati luksuzne nepremičnine v vročem Miamiju. Od plaže do sejne sobe, serija sledi Katrini in njeni ekipi nepremičninskih agentov med raziskovanjem najbolj luksuznih nepremičnin v Miamiju.

This reality series features the life and business of Katrina Campins, former "Apprentice" star and successful high-end Miami real estate agent. Campins caters to over 350 A-list celebrities, athletes and wealthy professionals, including Russell Brand, Katy Perry and Justin Timberlake. She runs her business with her charming ex-husband, her controlling Cuban mother and her younger sister. Viewers get an inside look at the drama behind helping high-end clients buy and sell luxury real estate in sultry Miami. From the beach to the boardroom, the series will follow Katrina and her team of realtors as they explore Miami's most luxurious properties.

Smrti zvezdnikov so, podobno kot njihova življenja, lahko sporne, neverjetne in dramatične. Ko zvezdnik umre, vse, kar je dosegel v svojem življenju, ostane. Raziskali bomo smrti nekaterih zvezdnikov in kaj se je zgodilo z njihovim denarjem. Presenečenja nikoli niso daleč, kadar gre za zvezdnike. Ta odlična serija predstavlja, kdo je hotel terjati dediščino, kdo jo je dejansko dobil, kateri zvezdniki, ki so živeli razkošna življenja, so umrli brez prebite pare in kateri zvezdniki se tudi leta po svoji smrti uvrščajo na sezname najbolje plačanih ljudi.

Celebrities’ deaths—much like their lives—can be controversial, fascinating and full of drama. When a celebrity dies, everything they’ve amassed during their lives—their fame, their accomplishments, and their possessions, stays behind. Celebrities Legacies explores what happens to these possessions. We explore the deaths of these celebrities and the big money involved in their passing. Surprises are always around the corner when stars are involved. This fascinating series details who tried to lay claim to the inheritance, who actually got it, what lavish-living celebrities really died penniless, and which celebrities are still making the highest-paid lists years after their deaths.

Najbolj znana ženitna posrednica na svetu se je vrnila boljša kot kdajkoli prej! V tej sezoni Zmenkov milijonarjev Patti Stanger in njena ekipa ljubezenskih gurujev prevzame hotel Luxe in se loti najtežjih primerov ženitnega posredovanja. Vsak teden se bosta dve od najbolj zahtevnih strank prijavili v ekskluzivni Klub milijonarjev. Patti bo skupaj s svojima najboljšima posrednikoma Candace in Maxwellom vodila milijonarje skozi intenzivni petdnevni tečaj o težavah na zmenkih in pri iskanju prave ljubezni. Tretjo generacijo posrednikov čaka težko delo, saj jo stranke, vključno s seksi zvezdniki iz Real Housewives in The Bachelor, ne ubogajo. Bodo s pomočjo bolečih ampak iskrenih nasvetov milijonarji odšli iz hotela sami ali z novo ljubeznijo?

The world’s most renowned matchmaker is back and better than ever! On this season on Million Dollar Matchmaker, Patti Stanger and her team of love gurus take over the Luxe Hotel to take on the toughest cases in matchmaking history yet. Each week, two of the most challenging clients will check into the exclusive Millionaire’s Club. Patti, along with her top matchmakers Candace and Maxwell, will guide the millionaires through an intensive, five day, crash course to work through their dating issues and to find true love. The third generation matchmaker has her work cut out for her when clients including sexy singles from The Real Housewives and The Bachelor don’t abide by her rules! With tougher love and some much needed reality checks, will the millionaires check out alone or with a new found flame?

Sobotni večeri v Las Vegasu gostijo eno izmed najbolj vročih in tekmovalnih kulinaričnih bitk v državi, ki je bila skrita očem javnosti vse do zdaj! V tem edinstvenem tekmovanju se dva izmed najbolj priznanih šefov v Las Vegasu pomerita v kulinarični igri epikurejskih dimenzij. Uporabila bosta raznolike in eksotične sestavine, ki so jih pozabili krajevni ulični prodajalci hrane, prav tako bosta tovornjakom s hrano dovolila, da vstopijo v njuni odlično opremljeni in ogromni kuhinji, kjer bo vsak poskušal premagati svojega nasprotnika. Izjemne jedi bodo predstavljene dvema strokovnima sodnikoma, zmagovalec pa bo domov odnesel pravico do hvaljenja in čudovito trofejo!

Saturday nights in Las Vegas host one of the hottest, most competitive culinary battles in the country... Hidden from the public eye, until now! In this self-contained food competition format, two of Las Vegas's most elite, five-star chefs engage in a culinary game of epicurean proportions. Using a diverse and exotic range of ingredients left behind by local food truck vendors, these chefs leave their well-equipped, massive kitchens to enter never-before-seen food trucks where they will try to outwit, out-create and out-cook their rival. Extraordinary dishes are conceived and presented to two expert judges, with the winner taking home the ultimate Vegas foodie bragging rights and one fabulously large trophy!

Kaj se zgodi, ko vzamete enega najboljših kuharjev v državi in ga združite s 24 nekdanjimi zaporniki, brez kuharskih izkušenj ter jim daste tri tedne časa, da odprejo vrhunsko restavracijo? Pridružite se svetovno znanemu kuharskemu mojstru Marcu Thuetu ter njegovi ženi in poslovni partnerici Biani Zorich, ki zastavita svoj ugled za visokoleteči izziv, ki bo njiju in njune učence prignal do skrajnosti.

What do you get when you take one of the country’s top chefs, throw in 24 ex-cons with no culinary experience, and give them just three weeks to open a high-end restaurant from scratch? Join world-renowned executive chef Marc Thuet and his wife and business partner Biana Zorich as they put their reputations on the line with a high-stakes challenge that will push them—and their charges—to the limit.

Biti oče in partner v sveži zvezi, povrhu pa še načrtovati dogodke za petične zvezdnike je neizprosno, a Davidu Tuteri vseeno uspeva. Oborožen s svojim prepoznavnim stilom, hitro jezo in prebrisanostjo mora organizirati rodee za petdesetletnike, zabave za predstavitev spodnjega perila in družinska zbiranja sredstev. Vedno pa ga čaka težavna naloga, saj mora spremeniti divje zahteve strank v epske zabave.

Juggling fatherhood and a new relationship while orchestrating events for diva-ish celebs is tough, but if anyone can do it, David Tutera can. With 50th birthday rodeos, spectacular lingerie launches and family fundraisers to organise, and armed only with his trademark style, wit and short fuse, David’s got a real job on his hands turning wild demands into epic celebrations.

Pridružite se Shannen Doherty iz serije Beverly Hills 90210 in fotografu Kurtu Iswarienku ter si oglejte duhovito in dramatično serijo, polno izzivov, v kateri boste spoznali dva človeka z dvema različnima ozadjema, ki stopita na skupno pot. Toda to se ne bi zgodilo brez pomoči vztrajnih prijateljev in sorodnikov. Njuna zapletena in pogosto izjemno duhovita zgodba je polna zvezdniškega življenjskega sloga, vključno s pripravami na poroko, tragedijo, po kateri grozijo tožbe, in naslednjim poglavjem igralkine kariere.

Join Beverly Hills, 90210's Shannen Doherty and fiancé photographer Kurt Iswarienko for a challenging, comical, and dramatic series about two people – with two different backgrounds – coming together. But not without a little help from their opinionated friends and family. Their complicated, often hilarious, story is a picture of modern celebrity lifestyle, including wedding preparations, a house tragedy that threatens lawsuits, and the next chapter of the actress’ burgeoning career.

V seriji Polnočna pojedina vam bo italijanski oddelek za hrano v New Yorku predstavil epski polnočni kulinarični obračun med nekaterimi najboljšimi vrhunskimi kuharji v državi. V vsaki edinstveni epizodi se bodo štirje kuharji pomerili v treh krogih z izločanjem, v katerih bodo morali pripraviti predjed, glavno jed in sladico. V vsakem krogu bodo kuharji imeli na voljo katerekoli sestavine, ki jih bodo našli na oddelku s hrano in zelo malo časa za načrtovanje in pripravo jedi. Po vsakem krogu bodo sodniki ocenili jedi glede na predstavitev, okus in ustvarjalnost ter izločili enega kuharja iz tekmovanja. Na koncu bo zmagovalec dobil denarno nagrado, ki predstavlja dvojno vrednost njegovega računa, poraženec pa bo moral plačati svoj račun. Ker imajo dostop do najboljših sestavin na svetu, mora vsak kuhar premisliti, ali je vredno tvegati in pripravljati jedi s temi dragimi in eksotičnimi sestavinami, saj ga sotekmovalec lahko porazi. Samo najbolj drzni in ustvarjalni kuharji bodo lahko premagali tri nasprotnike v treh krogih in si zaslužili slavo in denarno nagrado. Spremljali boste najbolj zahtevno bitko bistrih umov, ustvarjalnosti in veščin, ki jo je kulinarični svet kadarkoli videl.

In MIDNIGHT FEAST, a NYC food-hall (think Eataly) sets the stage for an epic late-night culinary showdown between some of the hottest professional chefs in the country. In each stand-alone episode, 4 chefs go head to head in 3 rounds of elimination: "munchies", "main", and "sweets." In each round, the chefs are given free rein to use any ingredient found in the food hall but have minimal time to plan and execute each dish. After each round, the judges critique the dishes based on presentation, taste, and creativity and cut one chef from the competition. By the end of the night, the winner walks away with a cash prize (twice the cost of their grocery bill!) while the losers walk away paying their own tabs. With access to the finest ingredients in the world, each chef must weigh their desire to use the most expensive and exotic ingredients against the risk of picking up an outlandish bill. Only the most daring and creative chefs will be able to beat three rivals over three courses to win glory and a cash prize. It's the most grueling battle of wits, creativity and skill the food world has ever seen.

It's the most grueling battle of wits, creativity and skill the food world has ever seen.

Najbolj znana ženitna posrednica na svetu se je vrnila boljša kot kdajkoli prej! V tej sezoni Zmenkov milijonarjev Patti Stanger in njena ekipa ljubezenskih gurujev prevzame hotel Luxe in se loti najtežjih primerov ženitnega posredovanja. Vsak teden se bosta dve od najbolj zahtevnih strank prijavili v ekskluzivni Klub milijonarjev. Patti bo skupaj s svojima najboljšima posrednikoma Candace in Maxwellom vodila milijonarje skozi intenzivni petdnevni tečaj o težavah na zmenkih in pri iskanju prave ljubezni. Tretjo generacijo posrednikov čaka težko delo, saj jo stranke, vključno s seksi zvezdniki iz Real Housewives in The Bachelor, ne ubogajo. Bodo s pomočjo bolečih ampak iskrenih nasvetov milijonarji odšli iz hotela sami ali z novo ljubeznijo?

The world’s most renowned matchmaker is back and better than ever! On this season on Million Dollar Matchmaker, Patti Stanger and her team of love gurus take over the Luxe Hotel to take on the toughest cases in matchmaking history yet. Each week, two of the most challenging clients will check into the exclusive Millionaire’s Club. Patti, along with her top matchmakers Candace and Maxwell, will guide the millionaires through an intensive, five day, crash course to work through their dating issues and to find true love. The third generation matchmaker has her work cut out for her when clients including sexy singles from The Real Housewives and The Bachelor don’t abide by her rules! With tougher love and some much needed reality checks, will the millionaires check out alone or with a new found flame?

Hiša proti hiši je tekmovalna serija, ki spremlja preobrazbe domov, kjer lahko amaterji in strokovnjaki osvojijo nagrado 10.000 dolarjev, tako da dokažejo, da lahko sami preuredijo svoj dom. Jim bo uspelo s pleskanjem, dekoriranjem in ostalimi deli priti do unikatnega in domiselnega doma? V vsaki epizodi se bosta dve ekipi pomerili v različnih izzivih, povezanih s preobrazbo doma. Tanya McQueen, poznana strokovnjakinja, in David Brian Sanders, arhitekt in oblikovalec, bosta odločila, katera skupina je opravila boljše delo in osvojila denarno nagrado.

House vs. House is a home makeover competition series where amateur and experienced renovation teams compete for the chance to win $10,000 by proving they can create the better DIY projects in their home. From painting and decorating, to one-of-a-kind, imaginative projects. In each episode, two teams will go head-to-head in grueling home makeover challenges. Tanya McQueen, a known expert in DIY design, and David Brian Sanders, an architect and designer, will determine which team completes the most impressive transformation and award the cash prize.

Kaj se zgodi, ko vzamete enega najboljših kuharjev v državi in ga združite s 24 nekdanjimi zaporniki, brez kuharskih izkušenj ter jim daste tri tedne časa, da odprejo vrhunsko restavracijo? Pridružite se svetovno znanemu kuharskemu mojstru Marcu Thuetu ter njegovi ženi in poslovni partnerici Biani Zorich, ki zastavita svoj ugled za visokoleteči izziv, ki bo njiju in njune učence prignal do skrajnosti.

What do you get when you take one of the country’s top chefs, throw in 24 ex-cons with no culinary experience, and give them just three weeks to open a high-end restaurant from scratch? Join world-renowned executive chef Marc Thuet and his wife and business partner Biana Zorich as they put their reputations on the line with a high-stakes challenge that will push them—and their charges—to the limit.

Biti oče in partner v sveži zvezi, povrhu pa še načrtovati dogodke za petične zvezdnike je neizprosno, a Davidu Tuteri vseeno uspeva. Oborožen s svojim prepoznavnim stilom, hitro jezo in prebrisanostjo mora organizirati rodee za petdesetletnike, zabave za predstavitev spodnjega perila in družinska zbiranja sredstev. Vedno pa ga čaka težavna naloga, saj mora spremeniti divje zahteve strank v epske zabave.

Juggling fatherhood and a new relationship while orchestrating events for diva-ish celebs is tough, but if anyone can do it, David Tutera can. With 50th birthday rodeos, spectacular lingerie launches and family fundraisers to organise, and armed only with his trademark style, wit and short fuse, David’s got a real job on his hands turning wild demands into epic celebrations.

V tej resničnostni oddaji spremljamo življenje in posle Katrine Campins, nekdanje zvezde oddaje "Apprentice" in vrhunske nepremičninske agentke iz Miamija. Campinsova skrbi za več kot 350 znanih osebnosti, za športnike in bogate zvezdnike kot so Russell Brand, Katy Perry in Justin Timberlake. Posle vodi z očarljivim bivšim možem, nadzorovalno kubansko mamo in s svojo mlajšo sestro. Gledalci dobijo vpogled v dramo, ki se odvija med delom, ko pomaga strankam kupiti in prodati luksuzne nepremičnine v vročem Miamiju. Od plaže do sejne sobe, serija sledi Katrini in njeni ekipi nepremičninskih agentov med raziskovanjem najbolj luksuznih nepremičnin v Miamiju.

This reality series features the life and business of Katrina Campins, former "Apprentice" star and successful high-end Miami real estate agent. Campins caters to over 350 A-list celebrities, athletes and wealthy professionals, including Russell Brand, Katy Perry and Justin Timberlake. She runs her business with her charming ex-husband, her controlling Cuban mother and her younger sister. Viewers get an inside look at the drama behind helping high-end clients buy and sell luxury real estate in sultry Miami. From the beach to the boardroom, the series will follow Katrina and her team of realtors as they explore Miami's most luxurious properties.

V seriji Polnočna pojedina vam bo italijanski oddelek za hrano v New Yorku predstavil epski polnočni kulinarični obračun med nekaterimi najboljšimi vrhunskimi kuharji v državi. V vsaki edinstveni epizodi se bodo štirje kuharji pomerili v treh krogih z izločanjem, v katerih bodo morali pripraviti predjed, glavno jed in sladico. V vsakem krogu bodo kuharji imeli na voljo katerekoli sestavine, ki jih bodo našli na oddelku s hrano in zelo malo časa za načrtovanje in pripravo jedi. Po vsakem krogu bodo sodniki ocenili jedi glede na predstavitev, okus in ustvarjalnost ter izločili enega kuharja iz tekmovanja. Na koncu bo zmagovalec dobil denarno nagrado, ki predstavlja dvojno vrednost njegovega računa, poraženec pa bo moral plačati svoj račun. Ker imajo dostop do najboljših sestavin na svetu, mora vsak kuhar premisliti, ali je vredno tvegati in pripravljati jedi s temi dragimi in eksotičnimi sestavinami, saj ga sotekmovalec lahko porazi. Samo najbolj drzni in ustvarjalni kuharji bodo lahko premagali tri nasprotnike v treh krogih in si zaslužili slavo in denarno nagrado. Spremljali boste najbolj zahtevno bitko bistrih umov, ustvarjalnosti in veščin, ki jo je kulinarični svet kadarkoli videl.

"Renovation Row" is a format that pits four talented renovation couples against each other in an on-trend transformation showdown. We will cast a town or city - from Buffalo to Baltimore - that is on the verge of becoming "the next big thing." Each couple will be given one rowhouse to renovate over the course of our series. While living inside these dilapidated homes our couple will use a designated budget to re-do key rooms and spaces in each self-contained episode. The final goal is to increase the overall value of the home by as much as they can. In the finale, the couples will stage an open house for their homes, and our neighborhood families - who have been spying on these newcomers and sharing their opinions with them all along - will have a chance to see the new homes on their street and witness which couple has increased the value to the max.

Smrti zvezdnikov so, podobno kot njihova življenja, lahko sporne, neverjetne in dramatične. Ko zvezdnik umre, vse, kar je dosegel v svojem življenju, ostane. Raziskali bomo smrti nekaterih zvezdnikov in kaj se je zgodilo z njihovim denarjem. Presenečenja nikoli niso daleč, kadar gre za zvezdnike. Ta odlična serija predstavlja, kdo je hotel terjati dediščino, kdo jo je dejansko dobil, kateri zvezdniki, ki so živeli razkošna življenja, so umrli brez prebite pare in kateri zvezdniki se tudi leta po svoji smrti uvrščajo na sezname najbolje plačanih ljudi.

Celebrities’ deaths—much like their lives—can be controversial, fascinating and full of drama. When a celebrity dies, everything they’ve amassed during their lives—their fame, their accomplishments, and their possessions, stays behind. Celebrities Legacies explores what happens to these possessions. We explore the deaths of these celebrities and the big money involved in their passing. Surprises are always around the corner when stars are involved. This fascinating series details who tried to lay claim to the inheritance, who actually got it, what lavish-living celebrities really died penniless, and which celebrities are still making the highest-paid lists years after their deaths.

V seriji Polnočna pojedina vam bo italijanski oddelek za hrano v New Yorku predstavil epski polnočni kulinarični obračun med nekaterimi najboljšimi vrhunskimi kuharji v državi. V vsaki edinstveni epizodi se bodo štirje kuharji pomerili v treh krogih z izločanjem, v katerih bodo morali pripraviti predjed, glavno jed in sladico. V vsakem krogu bodo kuharji imeli na voljo katerekoli sestavine, ki jih bodo našli na oddelku s hrano in zelo malo časa za načrtovanje in pripravo jedi. Po vsakem krogu bodo sodniki ocenili jedi glede na predstavitev, okus in ustvarjalnost ter izločili enega kuharja iz tekmovanja. Na koncu bo zmagovalec dobil denarno nagrado, ki predstavlja dvojno vrednost njegovega računa, poraženec pa bo moral plačati svoj račun. Ker imajo dostop do najboljših sestavin na svetu, mora vsak kuhar premisliti, ali je vredno tvegati in pripravljati jedi s temi dragimi in eksotičnimi sestavinami, saj ga sotekmovalec lahko porazi. Samo najbolj drzni in ustvarjalni kuharji bodo lahko premagali tri nasprotnike v treh krogih in si zaslužili slavo in denarno nagrado. Spremljali boste najbolj zahtevno bitko bistrih umov, ustvarjalnosti in veščin, ki jo je kulinarični svet kadarkoli videl.

In MIDNIGHT FEAST, a NYC food-hall (think Eataly) sets the stage for an epic late-night culinary showdown between some of the hottest professional chefs in the country. In each stand-alone episode, 4 chefs go head to head in 3 rounds of elimination: "munchies", "main", and "sweets." In each round, the chefs are given free rein to use any ingredient found in the food hall but have minimal time to plan and execute each dish. After each round, the judges critique the dishes based on presentation, taste, and creativity and cut one chef from the competition. By the end of the night, the winner walks away with a cash prize (twice the cost of their grocery bill!) while the losers walk away paying their own tabs. With access to the finest ingredients in the world, each chef must weigh their desire to use the most expensive and exotic ingredients against the risk of picking up an outlandish bill. Only the most daring and creative chefs will be able to beat three rivals over three courses to win glory and a cash prize. It's the most grueling battle of wits, creativity and skill the food world has ever seen.

Pridružite se Shannen Doherty iz serije Beverly Hills 90210 in fotografu Kurtu Iswarienku ter si oglejte duhovito in dramatično serijo, polno izzivov, v kateri boste spoznali dva človeka z dvema različnima ozadjema, ki stopita na skupno pot. Toda to se ne bi zgodilo brez pomoči vztrajnih prijateljev in sorodnikov. Njuna zapletena in pogosto izjemno duhovita zgodba je polna zvezdniškega življenjskega sloga, vključno s pripravami na poroko, tragedijo, po kateri grozijo tožbe, in naslednjim poglavjem igralkine kariere.

Join Beverly Hills, 90210's Shannen Doherty and fiancé photographer Kurt Iswarienko for a challenging, comical, and dramatic series about two people – with two different backgrounds – coming together. But not without a little help from their opinionated friends and family. Their complicated, often hilarious, story is a picture of modern celebrity lifestyle, including wedding preparations, a house tragedy that threatens lawsuits, and the next chapter of the actress’ burgeoning career.

Sobotni večeri v Las Vegasu gostijo eno izmed najbolj vročih in tekmovalnih kulinaričnih bitk v državi, ki je bila skrita očem javnosti vse do zdaj! V tem edinstvenem tekmovanju se dva izmed najbolj priznanih šefov v Las Vegasu pomerita v kulinarični igri epikurejskih dimenzij. Uporabila bosta raznolike in eksotične sestavine, ki so jih pozabili krajevni ulični prodajalci hrane, prav tako bosta tovornjakom s hrano dovolila, da vstopijo v njuni odlično opremljeni in ogromni kuhinji, kjer bo vsak poskušal premagati svojega nasprotnika. Izjemne jedi bodo predstavljene dvema strokovnima sodnikoma, zmagovalec pa bo domov odnesel pravico do hvaljenja in čudovito trofejo!

Saturday nights in Las Vegas host one of the hottest, most competitive culinary battles in the country... Hidden from the public eye, until now! In this self-contained food competition format, two of Las Vegas's most elite, five-star chefs engage in a culinary game of epicurean proportions. Using a diverse and exotic range of ingredients left behind by local food truck vendors, these chefs leave their well-equipped, massive kitchens to enter never-before-seen food trucks where they will try to outwit, out-create and out-cook their rival. Extraordinary dishes are conceived and presented to two expert judges, with the winner taking home the ultimate Vegas foodie bragging rights and one fabulously large trophy!

Najbolj znana ženitna posrednica na svetu se je vrnila boljša kot kdajkoli prej! V tej sezoni Zmenkov milijonarjev Patti Stanger in njena ekipa ljubezenskih gurujev prevzame hotel Luxe in se loti najtežjih primerov ženitnega posredovanja. Vsak teden se bosta dve od najbolj zahtevnih strank prijavili v ekskluzivni Klub milijonarjev. Patti bo skupaj s svojima najboljšima posrednikoma Candace in Maxwellom vodila milijonarje skozi intenzivni petdnevni tečaj o težavah na zmenkih in pri iskanju prave ljubezni. Tretjo generacijo posrednikov čaka težko delo, saj jo stranke, vključno s seksi zvezdniki iz Real Housewives in The Bachelor, ne ubogajo. Bodo s pomočjo bolečih ampak iskrenih nasvetov milijonarji odšli iz hotela sami ali z novo ljubeznijo?

The world’s most renowned matchmaker is back and better than ever! On this season on Million Dollar Matchmaker, Patti Stanger and her team of love gurus take over the Luxe Hotel to take on the toughest cases in matchmaking history yet. Each week, two of the most challenging clients will check into the exclusive Millionaire’s Club. Patti, along with her top matchmakers Candace and Maxwell, will guide the millionaires through an intensive, five day, crash course to work through their dating issues and to find true love. The third generation matchmaker has her work cut out for her when clients including sexy singles from The Real Housewives and The Bachelor don’t abide by her rules! With tougher love and some much needed reality checks, will the millionaires check out alone or with a new found flame?

Join Beverly Hills, 90210's Shannen Doherty and fiancé photographer Kurt Iswarienko for a challenging, comical, and dramatic series about two people – with two different backgrounds – coming together. But not without a little help from their opinionated friends and family. Their complicated, often hilarious, story is a picture of modern celebrity lifestyle, including wedding preparations, a house tragedy that threatens lawsuits, and the next chapter of the actress’ burgeoning career.

Da bi naredili prvi korak v svet nepremičnin, prvotne kupce ponavadi zanimajo soseske, ki so izgubile svoj ugled. Njihova ustvarjalnost vodi v obnovo krajevnih sosesk, jih iz pozabljenih spremeni v izjemne in jim tako povrne ponos ter njihovo vrednost v skupnosti, ki jih obdaja. V seriji bomo spremljali štiri nadarjene pare, ki bodo tekmovali med seboj v modernih prenovah domov. Poiskali bomo mesto ali kraj, od Buffala do Baltimora, ki je na samem robu uspeha. Vsak par bo dobil v prenovo vrstno hišo. V tem času bo živel v zapuščenem domu in dobil omejena sredstva, da bo lahko preuredil prostore. Končni cilj je povečati vrednost doma, kolikor je to le mogoče. Na koncu pa bodo pari pokazali svoje delo sosedom, ki so ves čas vohunili in ugotavljali, kateri par se je odrezal najbolje.

To take that first critical step onto the property ladder, first-time homebuyers often explore neighborhoods that have lost their luster. Their creativity leads the renovation of local neighborhoods, taking them from forgotten, to fabulous, and restoring the pride and property value of the community surrounding them. "Renovation Row" is a format that pits four talented renovation couples against each other in an on-trend transformation showdown. We will cast a town or city - from Buffalo to Baltimore - that is on the verge of becoming "the next big thing." Each couple will be given one rowhouse to renovate over the course of our series. While living inside these dilapidated homes our couple will use a designated budget to re-do key rooms and spaces in each self-contained episode. The final goal is to increase the overall value of the home by as much as they can. In the finale, the couples will stage an open house for their homes, and our neighborhood families - who have been spying on these newcomers and sharing their opinions with them all along - will have a chance to see the new homes on their street and witness which couple has increased the value to the max.

Biti oče in partner v sveži zvezi, povrhu pa še načrtovati dogodke za petične zvezdnike je neizprosno, a Davidu Tuteri vseeno uspeva. Oborožen s svojim prepoznavnim stilom, hitro jezo in prebrisanostjo mora organizirati rodee za petdesetletnike, zabave za predstavitev spodnjega perila in družinska zbiranja sredstev. Vedno pa ga čaka težavna naloga, saj mora spremeniti divje zahteve strank v epske zabave.

Juggling fatherhood and a new relationship while orchestrating events for diva-ish celebs is tough, but if anyone can do it, David Tutera can. With 50th birthday rodeos, spectacular lingerie launches and family fundraisers to organise, and armed only with his trademark style, wit and short fuse, David’s got a real job on his hands turning wild demands into epic celebrations.

V seriji Polnočna pojedina vam bo italijanski oddelek za hrano v New Yorku predstavil epski polnočni kulinarični obračun med nekaterimi najboljšimi vrhunskimi kuharji v državi. V vsaki edinstveni epizodi se bodo štirje kuharji pomerili v treh krogih z izločanjem, v katerih bodo morali pripraviti predjed, glavno jed in sladico. V vsakem krogu bodo kuharji imeli na voljo katerekoli sestavine, ki jih bodo našli na oddelku s hrano in zelo malo časa za načrtovanje in pripravo jedi. Po vsakem krogu bodo sodniki ocenili jedi glede na predstavitev, okus in ustvarjalnost ter izločili enega kuharja iz tekmovanja. Na koncu bo zmagovalec dobil denarno nagrado, ki predstavlja dvojno vrednost njegovega računa, poraženec pa bo moral plačati svoj račun. Ker imajo dostop do najboljših sestavin na svetu, mora vsak kuhar premisliti, ali je vredno tvegati in pripravljati jedi s temi dragimi in eksotičnimi sestavinami, saj ga sotekmovalec lahko porazi. Samo najbolj drzni in ustvarjalni kuharji bodo lahko premagali tri nasprotnike v treh krogih in si zaslužili slavo in denarno nagrado. Spremljali boste najbolj zahtevno bitko bistrih umov, ustvarjalnosti in veščin, ki jo je kulinarični svet kadarkoli videl.

In MIDNIGHT FEAST, a NYC food-hall (think Eataly) sets the stage for an epic late-night culinary showdown between some of the hottest professional chefs in the country. In each stand-alone episode, 4 chefs go head to head in 3 rounds of elimination: "munchies", "main", and "sweets." In each round, the chefs are given free rein to use any ingredient found in the food hall but have minimal time to plan and execute each dish. After each round, the judges critique the dishes based on presentation, taste, and creativity and cut one chef from the competition. By the end of the night, the winner walks away with a cash prize (twice the cost of their grocery bill!) while the losers walk away paying their own tabs. With access to the finest ingredients in the world, each chef must weigh their desire to use the most expensive and exotic ingredients against the risk of picking up an outlandish bill. Only the most daring and creative chefs will be able to beat three rivals over three courses to win glory and a cash prize. It's the most grueling battle of wits, creativity and skill the food world has ever seen.

V tej resničnostni oddaji spremljamo življenje in posle Katrine Campins, nekdanje zvezde oddaje "Apprentice" in vrhunske nepremičninske agentke iz Miamija. Campinsova skrbi za več kot 350 znanih osebnosti, za športnike in bogate zvezdnike kot so Russell Brand, Katy Perry in Justin Timberlake. Posle vodi z očarljivim bivšim možem, nadzorovalno kubansko mamo in s svojo mlajšo sestro. Gledalci dobijo vpogled v dramo, ki se odvija med delom, ko pomaga strankam kupiti in prodati luksuzne nepremičnine v vročem Miamiju. Od plaže do sejne sobe, serija sledi Katrini in njeni ekipi nepremičninskih agentov med raziskovanjem najbolj luksuznih nepremičnin v Miamiju.

This reality series features the life and business of Katrina Campins, former "Apprentice" star and successful high-end Miami real estate agent. Campins caters to over 350 A-list celebrities, athletes and wealthy professionals, including Russell Brand, Katy Perry and Justin Timberlake. She runs her business with her charming ex-husband, her controlling Cuban mother and her younger sister. Viewers get an inside look at the drama behind helping high-end clients buy and sell luxury real estate in sultry Miami. From the beach to the boardroom, the series will follow Katrina and her team of realtors as they explore Miami's most luxurious properties.
